<L>__{interior bela's hospital room day}
<A>__{bela lies sleeping in bed, pasty and pale. newspaper clippings of his hospital stay are tacked up. ed anxiously tiptoes in. he quietly speaks.}
<C>__{ed}
<D>__{bela, wake up.}
<A>__{bela stirs lethargically. ed puts on a fake smile.}
<C>__{ed}
<D>__{i've got some good news. the doctor says you're all better. you can come home.}
<C>__{bela}
<P>__{(so weak, he's barely audible)}
<D>__{really? i don't feel so great.}
<C>__{ed}
<D>__{no, you look good. and the tests came back fine.}
<P>__{(a poignant pause)}
<D>__{c'mon...}
<A>__{ed gingerly helps bela up.}
